1
00:00:05,344 --> 00:00:08,992
When we talk about 
Reality the Beautiful

2
00:00:09,113 --> 00:00:12,009
[God Can Too]

3
00:00:12,239 --> 00:00:15,591
it means reality: the all-love, 
the all-beautiful,

4
00:00:15,591 --> 00:00:21,418
the all-sweet, the all-charming, 
the all-accommodating, and all-personal.

5
00:00:21,418 --> 00:00:23,739
The Personality of Godhead.

6
00:00:23,739 --> 00:00:27,601
So, if a child in this world, 
a little baby …

7
00:00:27,601 --> 00:00:31,017
I was just in Phnom Penh 
in Cambodia,

8
00:00:31,017 --> 00:00:37,601
and one thing—you notice things about 
a place immediately when you’re visitor—

9
00:00:37,601 --> 00:00:40,685
there, children are a part of everything.

10
00:00:40,685 --> 00:00:42,934
Children are everywhere.

11
00:00:42,934 --> 00:00:50,685
Every night at around five o’clock 
they assemble on the riverfront

12
00:00:50,685 --> 00:00:55,736
and just spontaneously dance 
for an hour.

13
00:00:55,736 --> 00:00:59,601
Grandmas, little two-year-old, 
three-year-old kids,

14
00:00:59,601 --> 00:01:03,978
and everybody in-between, 
they all just get there and

15
00:01:03,978 --> 00:01:07,478
they put on some music 
and they dance for an hour.

16
00:01:07,478 --> 00:01:10,409
Two hundred, 
three hundred people.

17
00:01:10,409 --> 00:01:14,573
Just because they like to.

18
00:01:14,573 --> 00:01:16,542
And you see children.

19
00:01:16,542 --> 00:01:20,181
So those children … and you see 
little children crawling on the floor,

20
00:01:20,181 --> 00:01:26,980
they can hear, see, taste, 
touch, smell, and feel;

21
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:34,417
and search, and laugh, sing, dance—
they can do so many things.

22
00:01:34,417 --> 00:01:37,639
Should we think 
the original source

23
00:01:37,639 --> 00:01:42,155
of all such beings 
can’t do any of those things

24
00:01:42,155 --> 00:01:44,795
that a little human baby can do?

25
00:01:44,795 --> 00:01:51,377
The original source of all such babies 
and personalities can’t do those things—

26
00:01:51,377 --> 00:01:56,892
can’t see, hear, taste, touch, smell, 
feel, laugh, sing and dance?

27
00:01:56,892 --> 00:02:00,448
Why? 
Why should we think like that?

